Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.50,0:00:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样妥当吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.23,0:00:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让陛下独自前往诺齐亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是陛下的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.60,0:00:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那不怕死的个性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.44,0:00:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从以前就一直没变过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.92,0:00:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于度西斯的瓦解我至感悲痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.83,0:00:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.33,0:00:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是这封书简有交到您手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.43,0:00:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当初或许便能遏止\N度西斯的瓦解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.44,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带着记载了安那托勒对度西斯\N所表达的和平意愿的这封书简
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.61,0:00:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有两架先锋艇\N决定冒险飞越大风暴区…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.60,0:01:09.83,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.49,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.57,0:01:20.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说把黎明　当作是一个开始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.84,0:01:27.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说现在就是来临的时刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.85,0:01:32.38,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,与你的烟云时代交响曲\N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.46,0:01:41.76,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飞向云海的彼端　飞往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}雲の海の向こうに　光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.37,0:01:56.73,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇见有如魔法的那一刻？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.81,0:02:04.02,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.09,0:02:11.12,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩展翅飞翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.19,0:02:22.07,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那尽头  抓住了永恒…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.81,0:02:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}苏菲亚升级\NPromotion Sophia
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是副本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.96,0:02:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正本已经与\N三位勇敢的先锋艇驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.43,0:02:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起消失在大风暴区当中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.66,0:02:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用先锋艇吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.93,0:02:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导致目前世界瓦解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.70,0:03:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是基尔特公会的无能与怠惰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若要打破基尔特公会的控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.74,0:03:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让国家能够\N以民意为依归来运作的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了我们两国结成同盟外\N已别无其他办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.98,0:03:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是能结成同盟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又将由谁来担任盟主呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.22,0:03:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我来担任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨候鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们长久以来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.07,0:03:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直随着那些鸟群的向导\N对这片土地进行侵略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.28,0:03:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深怕在不久的将来\N度西斯即将为冰雪所封闭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.85,0:03:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些鸟能够为安那托勒的土地\N带来些许滋润的雨水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信雨候鸟所行经的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.83,0:04:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终将成为连结度西斯与\N安那托勒两个国家的和平之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.17,0:04:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这封书简我收下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.97,0:04:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这只被风雪伤得\N无法自由张开的粗手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.74,0:04:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您愿意和我握个手吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.39,0:04:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安那托勒和度西斯的婚礼是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就送些花给他们好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.97,0:04:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为…云层下实在好脏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.61,0:04:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到大风暴区当中\N居然有航路存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.95,0:04:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说度西斯在\N侵入安那托勒领空时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.62,0:05:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都会选择气流比较平稳的地点\N来穿越大风暴区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.76,0:05:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是从他们把\N这东西交给您这件事看来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.10,0:05:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便可充分得知\N度西斯也非常渴望和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.67,0:05:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此外还有一样东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涅斯特司令已经答应了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.34,0:05:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会全面协助我们找到EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是EXILE的动力音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定可以成为一个\N杰出的副舰长的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右满舵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.65,0:06:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮忙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.18,0:06:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从你开始进入引擎的修理后\N根本就没有进展嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.72,0:06:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.79,0:06:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过这部份还是让我自己来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.59,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这关系到\N小家伙能不能飞得起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是最重要的一个部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.40,0:06:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能亲手修好它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.91,0:07:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下我又能用这架来飞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用去舰桥吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.79,0:07:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.59,0:07:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是见鬼了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.86,0:07:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的小公主居然会说谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.92,0:07:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是待会儿拿去加菜啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.76,0:07:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸽子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.89,0:07:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是自由的象征耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作战日期已决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为山羊月13日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间0400
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问你\N你们度西斯都吃鸽子的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，吃了身体会很暖和哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.91,0:08:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.71,0:08:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，我害那鸽子逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.41,0:08:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫莫蓝．谢兰度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.68,0:08:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫多妮雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多妮雅．薛尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.95,0:08:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当天基尔特公会的年轻人\N在满17岁的这一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.12,0:08:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须向总帅宣誓效忠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.52,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔特全体人员会因这项\N盛大仪式而集合在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.36,0:08:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此这个宣誓日\N对我们联合军而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.86,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将会是一个最好的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.30,0:08:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这项作战当中\N先锋艇部队的位置十分的重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.27,0:08:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请各自牢牢记住这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你与我是两颗流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起变成流星吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.61,0:08:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.21,0:08:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离进行作战没有多少时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.05,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，要是没有这项\N夺取克劳地亚组件的作战计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们联合军是无法获得胜利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夺取组件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我们自己的手夺回我们的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:08:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这明明是我们的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.47,0:09:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么却不属于我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼他讨厌我了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许是刚才那段话\N说的不得体吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.45,0:09:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，是不是打扰你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.36,0:09:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.86,0:09:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，基尔特公会\N到底是个怎样的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.30,0:09:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言，迪奥殿下\N和总帅大人便代表了一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是基尔特公会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.20,0:09:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，很漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.27,0:09:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，找到一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.07,0:09:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.29,0:09:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是维修长给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我先来替您试毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.22,0:10:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我试过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉你也吃嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.76,0:10:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.43,0:10:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.53,0:10:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一股清爽的酸味\N与恰到好处的甜味弥漫口中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的时候\N就要做出好吃的表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表情…是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.91,0:10:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你好吃的表情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.66,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.23,0:10:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.83,0:10:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们听说了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫蓝他说要离开银之战舰耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.18,0:10:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这么说或许会有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.28,0:10:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我其实还满喜欢银之战舰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.52,0:11:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许我喜欢的…\N是从银之战舰上看见的天空吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.32,0:11:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你装什么诗人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.99,0:11:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了保护艾儿\N才登上银之战舰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.70,0:11:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然给拉薇添了不少麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但无论是对基尔特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是对银之战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都想保护她不受他们伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直误会了银之战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.58,0:11:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船确实是\N世界上最安全的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.28,0:11:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲亚，塔琪安娜\N还有维修科的大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.62,0:11:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是银之战舰在保护着艾儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.49,0:11:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我想通这点\N就同时看清了一件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银之战舰的船员们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.76,0:11:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都是飞翔在\N自己所选择的天空上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.80,0:11:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说\N我是不会离开银之战舰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可别死哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以对生还章发誓\N我是不会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.98,0:12:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么还带着那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.22,0:12:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是很有纪念价值的\N第20枚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.02,0:12:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要走吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.63,0:12:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我是枪兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么祝我们改日再相逢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.79,0:12:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当班人员各就各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是舰桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轮机室启动准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动组件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.40,0:13:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过热蒸汽开始注入汽缸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,齿轮传动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.24,0:13:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涡轮转动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.04,0:13:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳地亚开始加压
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.21,0:13:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,压力30%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动力输出上升中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.45,0:13:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组件，启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组件启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动力准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰尾离岸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰尾离岸完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰首离岸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.67,0:13:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两舷以最微速前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.14,0:13:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两舷最微速前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.14,0:13:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舵转中央
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.78,0:13:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰首离岸完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信号确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,读出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发自渥卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你幸运\N你赊的酒钱记得要付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银之战舰的回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒钱记在皇帝的帐上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，就这么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,航路安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.51,0:14:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银之战舰出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银之战舰出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.55,0:14:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.39,0:15:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会离开银之战舰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.23,0:15:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.59,0:15:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要以先锋艇驾驶员的身分\N留在这艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.63,0:15:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新皇帝的加冕仪式要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.67,0:15:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你驾先锋艇去做前导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.54,0:15:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.11,0:15:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替我去恭贺苏菲亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.51,0:17:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于此，新一代的皇帝陛下\N开启了新的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.08,0:17:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安那托勒与度西斯\N也将签下同盟之约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，是苏菲亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.73,0:17:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看起来好像变了一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.04,0:18:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼式回转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.53,0:18:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会这一招吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手，太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.23,0:18:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要庆祝吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就来一点花俏的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥殿下，冷静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了，来了，戴芬妮来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.52,0:19:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.72,0:19:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.55,0:19:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃，快逃，快逃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是基尔特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.37,0:19:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，请往这边走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.14,0:19:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.14,0:19:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是宣战布告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.78,0:19:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，我们上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.82,0:19:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.80,0:20:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，变得多漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.87,0:20:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总帅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认到迪奥殿下\N和鲁修拉的行踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.74,0:20:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一架行动异常的先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，迪奥是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.68,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跑到哪儿寄生去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.80,0:20:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.56,0:20:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加冕仪式会场上\N出现了基尔特战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方在到处洒落蔷薇花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.24,0:20:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轮机室，开到最大航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.87,0:20:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体人员进入战斗状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了…了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它击沈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.49,0:21:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下方有副舰长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.19,0:21:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.36,0:21:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.33,0:21:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个总帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.20,0:21:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您应该不是那种\N会株连同伴的人才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.70,0:21:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标，基尔特舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.11,0:21:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弹种穿甲弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.71,0:21:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炮击手，命令撤回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.04,0:21:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长现在不对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以听他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.81,0:21:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坎贝尔，你这家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.78,0:21:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.09,0:21:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您无论如何忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.02,0:21:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迟早一定会有攻击的机会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.18,0:22:40.34,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的时光逐渐逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.95,0:22:47.01,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你离我如此接近感觉  却好远…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く  でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.09,0:22:58.16,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什么  心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.23,0:23:03.76,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你舍命奋斗的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.84,0:23:12.54,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种透明的美丽  令我不禁哑口无言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.62,0:23:18.49,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飞往天际\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.55,0:23:24.29,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿成为你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.36,0:23:30.16,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,无论风有多么强\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.23,0:23:35.93,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永远不会折断的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.01,0:23:47.97,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我会拥有那样一对翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.45,0:23:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(下回预告)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.92,0:23:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，我把皇帝旗降下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.89,0:23:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还挺机灵的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.83,0:24:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，随时要懂得预测未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.10,0:24:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身处劣势时\N要将舰艇损害减到最小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.57,0:24:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身处优势时\N就要在敌人的小伤口上抹盐巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.34,0:24:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.27,0:24:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最后流亡 第19话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.88,0:24:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西西里式防御\NSicilian Defence
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.21,0:24:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.55,0:24:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要跟我交换副官啊
